criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Present age equal or superior to 60 years;

          -  Be a family member and primary caregiver of the patient with Alzheimer's disease for
             at least six months;

          -  To present independent walking ability.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Cardiopulmonary or orthopedic contraindication to the practice of physical exercise;

          -  Present severe visual or hearing deficiency.
